\begin_layout Standard
When playing this game in person, all that is needed is pen and paper, and
 five ordinary six-sided dice for each player including the Host.
 While optional, it would be very useful to keep a printout of this document
 on hand (or a computer/tablet you can easily access it with) and a printout
 of the character sheet for each player.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For online play, each player should have a copy of this document and a means
 to share character sheets and information with each other, such as Google
 Docs or Microsoft 365.
 In addition, you will need a means to roll dice – whether that is physical
 dice for each player, or a dice roller program or bot.
\end_layout

